Variables to keep:

Temporal information:

YEAR, QUARTER, MONTH, DAY_OF_MONTH, DAY_OF_WEEK, FL_DATE

Carrier and flight identifiers:

OP_UNIQUE_CARRIER, OP_CARRIER, OP_CARRIER_AIRLINE_ID, OP_CARRIER_FL_NUM, TAIL_NUM

Airport/location details:

ORIGIN, ORIGIN_CITY_NAME, ORIGIN_STATE_ABR

DEST, DEST_CITY_NAME, DEST_STATE_ABR

Scheduled and actual times:

CRS_DEP_TIME, DEP_TIME

WHEELS_OFF, WHEELS_ON

ARR_TIME

Delay and cancellation:

DEP_DELAY, DEP_DELAY_NEW, DEP_DEL15

ARR_DELAY, ARR_DELAY_NEW

CANCELLED, CANCELLATION_CODE

Flight time and distance:

ACTUAL_ELAPSED_TIME, AIR_TIME, DISTANCE

Delay causes (nalyzing causes):

CARRIER_DELAY, WEATHER_DELAY
